 increases astronomical conditions get better} (CC,\nPWV and AOD gets lower values). All the results will be made available online\nthrough astroGIS database.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Oct 2021 06:25:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-05"}
