 method can provide guidance for tabular\ndata analysis as well as the design of future surveys.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Oct 2021 12:51:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 7 Jan 2023 22:17:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-10"}
