ive: one from the conventional\nlinear, discrete wave models to the nonlinear wave models dealing with\ncontinuous spectra due to trapping and a second from the BGK to the present\nmethod for the correct handling of equilibria.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Oct 2021 13:21:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 10 Jan 2022 11:08:06 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 17 May 2022 10:21:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-18"}
